direction: down

User: {
  label: "**User**\nSpeaks / listens"
}

Capture: {
  label: "**Audio capture**\nMic or WAV file"
}

STT: {
  label: "**STT**\n(Option: Google Cloud STT v2 / Gemini audio)"
}

LLM: {
  label: "**DSPy / LLM calling**\n(Existing playground reference)"
}

TTS: {
  label: "**TTS**\n(Option: Cloud Text-to-Speech / Gemini audio)"
}

Playback: {
  label: "**Audio playback**\nSpeaker / output WAV"
}

User -> Capture -> STT -> LLM -> TTS -> Playback -> User
